		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Thanks thefox for the save state mappers.  I've been playing around with them and they are working great!
<br />
<br />Do you take feature requests?  
<br />
<br />Sometimes I press the wrong button, yes I'm dumb, and load a state when I actually wanted to save.  Do you think you can implement a feature where a message box pops up and asks you do you really want to load or save a state?  Maybe this message box can be turned on or off at the menu where you select turbo buttons.  Just a thought.
<br />
<br />Thanks!
<br />Mike

		

		</td>
	</tr>
